author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Ra Ra Riot featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2016.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Absolutely
00:03:51 Water
00:08:20 Foreign Lovers

Musicians
Wes Miles — vocals, keyboard
Milo Bonacci — guitar, keyboard
Matheiu Santos — bass, vocals
Rebecca Zeller — violin, vocals
Lavena Johanson — cello
Kenny Bernard — drums

Credits
Engineer – Michael DeMark, Sasha Druva
Producer – Derrick Stevens
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
